+# Ontarix — SEO & Contact Form Changes
+
+This patch adds:
+
+- Canonical URLs and JSON-LD to `about.html` and `capabilities.html`.
+- Canonical to `404.html`.
+- A Cloudflare Pages Function at `functions/api/contact.js` to handle form submissions and send email to `info@ontarix.ca` via Resend.
+
+## After merging
+
+1. **Cloudflare Pages → Settings → Environment variables (Production)**
+   - Add **Secret** `RESEND_API_KEY` (from Resend)
+   - Add **Secret** `TURNSTILE_SECRET` (from Cloudflare Turnstile, if you use the widget)
+
+2. **Resend**
+   - Add domain `ontarix.ca`, publish SPF/DKIM/DMARC DNS records in Cloudflare, and verify the domain.
+
+3. **Form markup**
+   - Ensure your form posts to `/api/contact` and includes fields `name`, `email`, `message`.
+   - (Recommended) Include the Turnstile widget and a hidden `company` honeypot field.
+
+4. **Google Search Console**
+   - Submit `https://www.ontarix.ca/sitemap.xml` and request indexing for key pages.
